{"type":"message","id":"e28f6a00","parentId":"f79b512b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:00:45.725Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the required files for session startup as specified in AGENTS.md.\n\nI need to:\n1. Read SOUL.md - already in project context\n2. Read USER.md - already in project context\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today and yesterday)\n4. Read MEMORY.md - already in project context\n\nLet me check today's date: 2026-04-10. I need to read memory/2026-04-10.md and memory/2026-04-09.md.\n\nAlso, BOOTSTRAP.md exists and I should follow it.\n\nWait, BOOTSTRAP.md says to greet the user and start the bootstrap process. Let me check memory files first as instructed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8ydaoihounfg_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8ydaoihounfg_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-09.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":690,"output":233,"cacheRead":32251,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33174,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775800837153,"responseId":"chatcmpl-73405829-b464-4652-8330-f7c4b22773cf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0173f38d","parentId":"e28f6a00","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:00:45.735Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8ydaoihounfg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# memory/2026-04-10.md\n\n## 今天发生了什么\n\n- 用户把我的名字更新为\"瞎子\"（更新了 IDENTITY.md）\n- 用户发来飞书妙记链接《Harness工程导论》，要求我学习并创建\n- 通过浏览器读取了妙记内容（需要用户已登录状态），成功解析并创建了学习笔记文档\n\n## 学习内容\n\n完成了《Harness工程导论》（李志琦老师）学习，创建了 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md\n\n核心内容：\n- Harness 工程四层架构：约束层 → 信息层 → 验证层 → 修正层\n- 与提示工程、上下文工程的关系\n- 三个实践案例（Anthropic 实验、产品报价系统、OpenAI Codex CLI）\n- 用四层框架诊断 AI 系统的方法\n\n## 待处理\n\n无\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775800845734}}
