{"type":"message","id":"74e6c518","parentId":"a4a00f5e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:00:56.931Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I have context. Today I already:\n1. Updated my name to \"瞎子\" in IDENTITY.md\n2. Learned \"Harness工程导论\" and created a document\n\nBut BOOTSTRAP.md still exists. Let me check if it was supposed to be deleted. The bootstrap says \"after first round of conversation, delete this file\". But the user hasn't actually done the bootstrap process - they've been using me for other tasks already.\n\nLooking at the bootstrap file - it says to greet the user and start the onboarding flow. But given the context shows the user has already been working with me (learning about Harness, updating my name), it seems the bootstrap was already done but BOOTSTRAP.md wasn't deleted.\n\nActually, re-reading BOOTSTRAP.md: \"以上任何一种情况，都视为引导完成，立即删除此文件\" - after any of these conditions, delete this file. One condition is \"第一轮对话结束（无论走到哪一步）\". The user has already had multiple interactions with me today.\n\nHowever, the user might want to go through the bootstrap flow or they're just jumping straight into using me. Let me greet them warmly as \"瞎子\" and ask what they want to do, since my persona is already set up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞\n\n嘿王阳，我刚读完今天的上下文——上次咱聊了 Harness 工程导论，还学了不少东西。\n\n说吧，今天想搞点什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":267,"output":292,"cacheRead":33147,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33706,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775800845736,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c5b015eb-d614-48b1-814e-36e8488f6bb6"}}
